chance of success.

43:24.102 --> 43:26.636
- What's that?

43:26.638 --> 43:28.871
- The<i> Lumen</i> will bring
the Master out of hiding.

43:28.873 --> 43:32.208
When he comes for it,
I'll kill him.

43:32.210 --> 43:35.778
- Why?
- My grievance is personal.

43:38.283 --> 43:40.249
- How do I know you can get
the job done?

43:40.251 --> 43:43.820
- I've been preparing
for this... job

43:43.822 --> 43:45.888
for over a thousand years.

43:45.890 --> 43:48.825
It's not what's in the book
that will destroy him,

43:48.827 --> 43:51.260
but what we do with it.

43:51.262 --> 43:53.329
You turn off

43:53.331 --> 43:55.565
the UV lights,

43:55.567 --> 43:58.568
that lock is child's play
for me.

43:58.570 --> 44:01.404
What do you say,
Dr. Goodweather?

44:01.406 --> 44:04.907
Together we can use the book

44:04.909 --> 44:07.043
to save the world...

44:09.247 --> 44:11.848
...and your son.

